<p>
	Sau ba s&aacute;ng, o&agrave;n i thm vn <strong>c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n Quc gia PuDaCuo</strong> (Ph t Th) , <strong>Vn quc gia Pudacuo</strong>, <strong>Shangri-la</strong>, V&acirc;n Nam: Thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n  <strong>Shangri-La</strong> xng &aacute;ng c mnh danh l&agrave; chn ti&ecirc;n cnh vi nhng cnh quan n&uacute;i cao tuyt trng, rng xanh nng v&agrave;ng, thi thong li n hin trong sng kh&oacute;i vi mt h ng thc vt v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng phong ph&uacute;. <strong>Pudacuo</strong> l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n quc gia u ti&ecirc;n  Trung Quc &aacute;p ng  c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u chun c thit lp bi T chc Bo tn Thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n Quc t (IUCN). Mt trong 40 thng cnh p ca Trung Quc.Pudacuo l&agrave; thi&ecirc;n ng cho nhng ngi y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch chp nh. Bn m&ugrave;a  &acirc;y cnh sc u kh&ocirc;ng ging nhau. M&ugrave;a xu&acirc;n  &acirc;y trm hoa ua n. M&ugrave;a h&egrave; l&agrave; mt m&agrave;u xanh bic ph y khp n&uacute;i. M&ugrave;a thu l&agrave; cnh rng rm tng tng v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng lng ly. M&ugrave;a &ocirc;ng du kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th thng thc cnh lp tuyt trng di mt h nc xanh.</p>
<p>
	Chiu t do tham quan Th&agrave;nh c DuKeZong. Sau &oacute; di chuyn v <strong>L Giang</strong>. Ngh ti <strong>L Giang</strong></p>
<h2>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#ff0000;"><strong>NG&Agrave;Y&nbsp; 05: L GIANG &ndash; C&Ocirc;N MINH&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(n s&aacute;ng, tra, ti)</strong></span></span></h2>
<p>
	n s&aacute;ng ti kh&aacute;ch sn, a o&agrave;n i n s&aacute;ng, sau &oacute; o&agrave;n khi h&agrave;nh i ti khu khu lch <strong>N&uacute;i Tuyt Ngc Long.</strong> Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch i c&aacute;p treo nh l&ecirc;n thm <strong>V&acirc;n Tam B&igrave;nh</strong> &ndash;  cao 3200 m ngm cnh p <strong>N&uacute;i tuyt Ngc Long</strong> - ngn n&uacute;i cao 5596 m tuyt ph quanh nm. Phn bng vnh cu &aacute;nh l&ecirc;n mt m&agrave;u xanh nh ngc. Li gi &acirc;y l&agrave; n&uacute;i trinh n v&igrave; cho n nay con ngi cha mt ln chinh phc c n&oacute;. Nhiu nh&agrave; leo n&uacute;i &atilde; b mng hoc ngm ng&ugrave;i r&uacute;t lui, bt lc trc s trinh nguy&ecirc;n b&iacute; n ca v&ugrave;ng n&uacute;i v&agrave;o loi p nht tnh V&acirc;n Nam n&agrave;y. Tham quan <strong>Bch Thy H&agrave;</strong> c to th&agrave;nh bi bng tan t n&uacute;i tuyt Ngc Long, <strong>tho nguy&ecirc;n Cam Hi T</strong>, thm <strong>Ngc Thy Tri</strong> &ndash; ni c&oacute; cnh p v&agrave; th hin tp tc, t&iacute;n ngng ca d&acirc;n Na Xi v&agrave; nn vn h&oacute;a &ocirc;ng Ba</p>
<p>
	Ti : Sau ba ti, ra ga l&ecirc;n t&agrave;u ho tuyn <strong>L Giang &ndash; C&ocirc;n Minh , K9684&nbsp; 21h50/06h41</strong> &nbsp;, ngh &ecirc;m tr&ecirc;n t&agrave;u ho ( <strong><em>ging nm khoang 6</em></strong> ) .</p>
