	Sau ba s&aacute;ng, o&agrave;n i <strong>Shangrila</strong>. Tr&ecirc;n ng gh&eacute; thm <strong>khe H Nhy</strong>, c xem l&agrave; hm n&uacute;i s&acirc;u nht Th Gii. &acirc;y l&agrave; mt hm n&uacute;i d&agrave;i hn 15 km nm kp gia hai <strong>d&atilde;y n&uacute;i Ngc Long Tuyt Sn</strong> (cao 5.596 m) v&agrave; <strong>Ha Ba Tuyt Sn</strong> (cao 5.396 m). Thm ch&ugrave;a&nbsp; <strong>Songzanlin</strong> l&agrave; tu vin Pht gi&aacute;o Mt T&ocirc;ng T&acirc;y Tng quan trng v&agrave; ln nht  V&acirc;n Nam, Trung Quc. Songzanlin c t trong mt cnh quan tuyt p   cao hn 3.300m c&aacute;ch Shangrila 5km.&nbsp;</p>
<h2>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#ff0000;"><strong>NG&Agrave;Y&nbsp; 04: SHANGRI-LA &ndash; L GIANG&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(n s&aacute;ng, tra, ti)</strong></span></span></h2>
<p>
