	<strong>S&aacute;ng:</strong> 08h35 t&agrave;u n L Giang, HDV a o&agrave;n i n s&aacute;ng, Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch thm quan <strong><em>C&ocirc;ng Vi&ecirc;n Hc Long &agrave;m</em></strong> &ndash; ni D&ograve;ng nc t <strong><em>n&uacute;i bng Ngc Long</em></strong>  v nu&ocirc;i sng v&ugrave;ng t L Giang. T c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n Hc Long c&oacute; th ngm s h&ugrave;ng v ca n&uacute;i tuyt ng&agrave;n nm, trong khung cnh thanh b&igrave;nh ca nc h phng lng.. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch gh&eacute; thm <strong><em>Mc Ph</em></strong>, <strong><em>Vn C Lu </em></strong>mt c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh c coi l&agrave; ti&ecirc;u biu cho lch s v&agrave; vn h&oacute;a ni &acirc;y. <strong><em>Mc ph</em></strong> c v&iacute; nh T Cm th&agrave;nh ca phng nam. Trc cng, d&ograve;ng nc chy t hng bc xung c bc ngang bi c&acirc;y cu &aacute; rng kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; th&agrave;nh. i din b&igrave;nh phong ngo&agrave;i l&agrave; t&ograve;a cng ch&agrave;o bng &aacute;. Xa kia t&ograve;a cng ch&agrave;o n&agrave;y l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh k v nht t L Giang, l&agrave;m bng &aacute; ngc trng,</p>
<p>
	Tham quan <strong><em>Th&agrave;nh c L Giang</em></strong> - x&acirc;y dng c&aacute;ch &acirc;y hn 800 nm, c <strong><em>Unessco</em></strong> c&ocirc;ng nhn l&agrave; di sn vn ho&aacute; th gii nm 1997- mt di sn vn h&oacute;a th gii vi phong cnh p  x nc, c mnh danh l&agrave; &quot;Venice ca Phng &ocirc;ng&quot;, ni &acirc;y nh&agrave; nh&agrave; u c&oacute; sui chy qua, nhng c&acirc;y liu bu&ocirc;ng xung c&aacute;c bc ca v&agrave; nhng c&acirc;y cu nh xinh xn. Do <strong><em>Ph T Phng</em></strong>  trung t&acirc;m th&agrave;nh c.</p>
<p>
	Sau khi d&ugrave;ng ba ti, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t do ngm sc m&agrave;u <strong><em>L Giang</em></strong> v &ecirc;m. T do thng thc c &acirc;m nhc v&agrave; c&aacute;c iu d&acirc;n v. Ph c L Giang c&ograve;n c&oacute; th gi l&agrave; ph ca &acirc;m nhc d&acirc;n tc v&agrave; d&acirc;n v m&agrave; bn chng cn tn mt xu tin v&eacute; li c&oacute; th tr th&agrave;nh din vi&ecirc;n ngay nu th&iacute;ch.. Ngh &ecirc;m ti <strong><em>L Giang</em></strong></p>
<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#ff0000;"><strong>NG&Agrave;Y 03: L GIANG &ndash; SHANGRI-LA&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(n s&aacute;ng, tra, ti)&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>
<p>
	Sau ba s&aacute;ng, o&agrave;n i <strong>Shangrila</strong>. Tr&ecirc;n ng gh&eacute; thm <strong>khe H Nhy</strong>, c xem l&agrave; hm n&uacute;i s&acirc;u nht Th Gii. &acirc;y l&agrave; mt hm n&uacute;i d&agrave;i hn 15 km nm kp gia hai <strong>d&atilde;y n&uacute;i Ngc Long Tuyt Sn</strong> (cao 5.596 m) v&agrave; <strong>Ha Ba Tuyt Sn</strong> (cao 5.396 m). Thm ch&ugrave;a&nbsp; <strong>Songzanlin</strong> l&agrave; tu vin Pht gi&aacute;o Mt T&ocirc;ng T&acirc;y Tng quan trng v&agrave; ln nht  V&acirc;n Nam, Trung Quc. Songzanlin c t trong mt cnh quan tuyt p   cao hn 3.300m c&aacute;ch Shangrila 5km.&nbsp;</p>
<h2>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#ff0000;"><strong>NG&Agrave;Y&nbsp; 04: SHANGRI-LA &ndash; L GIANG&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(n s&aacute;ng, tra, ti)</strong></span></span></h2>
<p>
