<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">
	<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Ng&agrave;y&nbsp; 05: PHNG HO&Agrave;NG &ndash; MI&Ecirc;U TRI - C&Aacute;T TH - NAM NINH (n s&aacute;ng, tra, ti)&nbsp;</span></span></h2>
<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">
